          <p>In addition to using the <italic toggle="yes">QQ</italic> ratio statistic, we also use a statistic that compares the on-cells' mean expression value with all cells' mean expression value. That is, we compare how much the mean of the alternative hypothesis shifts from the mean of the null hypothesis as follows.<disp-formula><tex-math id="M00033" notation="LaTeX">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
